RACE.RACE_TEXT: LONE STAR PARK RACE 1 6 1/2F Dirt CR: 83. Allowance Purse 11000. FOR THREE YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON TWO RACES. Three Year Olds, 119 lbs.; Older, 124 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: RB MALEXIS was rated along the rail while stalking the pace with outer rivals, then advanced three wide on the turn to vie for the lead, edge clear in the early stretch and was ridden out till the end. RB NASH BASH dueled with WMA GRAND FINAL down the backstretch and throughout the turn, then vied briefly entering the stretch before giving way in the end. WMA GRAND FINALE dueled while two wide down the backstretch and into the turn under a strong drive then flattened out in the stretch while drifting out late. SCORCHED stalked the dueling leaders while three wide, then bid from the four path on the turn and into the stretch and came up empty. BLAZING STAR AA stalked the pace while two wide then dropped back heading into the turn and was no threat.
